 This install applies to "Liquid Kids" © 1991 Ocean (unreleased).

 This install requires WHDLoad, DIC and RawDIC to be in the path.
 The programs can be found in the WHDLoad package.
 To install from a different drive than DF0: select installation mode Expert.

 The installed program requires 0.5 MB ChipMem and 0.5 MB OtherMem.
 It can be quit by pressing F10 (key can be changed with Tooltype "QuitKey=").

 If you have problems with this installation please try and get a newer
 version of this package from the WHDLoad WWW-Page. If that doesn't help try
 some Tooltypes like NOCACHE, NOAUTOVEC, EXPCHIP, NOMMU, PAL or NTSC. If
 that also fails, please inform the author via the Bug-Report-Form which
 can be accessed on the WHDLoad WWW-Page or create a mantis issue directly
 at http://mantis.whdload.de

 For the full WHDLoad package, other installs and updates refer to:
        http://www.whdload.de/
 or     aminet:dev/misc/whdload#?
 and    aminet:game/patch/

 version 1.2 (11.11.2019) done by JOTD
 - CUSTOM2=1 enables jumping using second button instead of up
 - Added joypad controls: play: pause/unpause, fwd+rev+play: quit whdload
 - you can force a language using CUSTOM4 tooltype (instead of CUSTOM2)
   CUSTOM4=1 : for english
   CUSTOM4=2 : for french
   CUSTOM4=3 : for german
   CUSTOM4=4 : for polish

 version 1.1 (29.04.2006) done by CFou!
 - Fixed to run with full cpu caches on 68060
 - Another missing blitter delays inserted in game and outro

 version 1.0 (12.11.2005) done by CFou!
 - initial release
 - Possiblility to install disk image or to extract files
 - Rawdic imager used only for file extraction
 - CUSTOM1=1 tooltype used to activate unlimited lives 
   CUSTOM1=2 to activate level skip key 'F8' during the game
   CUSTOM1=4 to see outro pressing 'F8' in game
   (you can cumulate different options by example: CUSTOM1=3 for 1+2 options)
 - Some engligh messages fixed (Thanx to Codetapper)
 - French, german & polish transations added (Thanks to CannivalPinHead & Janusz)
   if lowlevel.library is found in your OS, language is automatically set.
   (only for french, german and english)
   but you can force a language using CUSTOM2 tooltype
   CUSTOM2=1 : for english
   CUSTOM2=2 : for french
   CUSTOM2=3 : for german
   CUSTOM2=4 : for polish
 - Keyboard interrupt added to the intro and main title
 - Keyboard interrupt fixed during the game
 - 'F7' key used to kill yourself
 - Load/Save game redirected on HD (file 'highs')
   (save option only if trainer is not activated)
    press in game:
     1 - to Switch off/on Music
     2 - to Switch off/on SFX
     P - to switch off/on game pause
 - Many copper list problems fixed
 - Decrunch routines relocated in fast memory (ICE!)
 - Many blitter delays inserted
 - Source code included
 - Many colored icons added

PS: Game was been tested with full 'caches' Tooltype on Blizzard 030&060 + 32 Mo

